Continuing my goal to workout in every National Park! Redwoods, CHECK ✔️🌲
.
Here’s a fun, fast, full body workout challenge from my Home Body Guide 2.0! There is no equipment required for this training program, so it’s perfect if you prefer to workout from home or if you travel often, like me!
.
D E E T S :
.
Complete all reps of this workout as fast as you possibly can! Write your score down & save this workout so you can try it again in a couple weeks & try to beat your time! 💪
.
FOR TIME:
.
➖10 BURPEES
➖20 PUSH UPS
➖30 SIT UPS
➖40 AIR SQUATS
➖50 MTN CLIMBERS
➖40 AIR SQUATS
➖30 SIT UPS
➖20 PUSH UPS
➖10 BURPEES
.
Comment below your score & tag your workout homies who you challenge to crush it, too! 👊
.
What National Park should I workout in next?!
.
.
.

Currently bawling my eyes out because I’ve been waiting over a year for this day to come! 😭🙏
.
I poured SO much love, sweat, tears (& waffle mix 😉) into this cookbook & I am so very proud of what I created.
.
This is more than just a cookbook, though. On top of the 90 delicious, macro-friendly recipes, I also included my fit tips & quick & effective workouts that you can do from anywhere! Including your kitchen, or even your van if you’re like me! 🏠
.
Each recipe uses one simple, compact & not to mention cute, Dash mini waffle maker! If you’ve been here for awhile, you know how much I LOVE this thing!
.
My passion is to help as many people as possible create healthier relationships with food & fitness.
.
That’s why I created a cookbook filled with a wide variety of healthy, easy to make recipes full of amazing flavor, but not all the extra calories.
.
I used to believe that performing & looking my best, meant that I had to eat the same, boring basic foods over & over again. 
.
Then I found out the Dash mini waffle maker, & I discovered that cooking can actually be fun & that it is possible to LOVE food & LOVE my body at the same time! 💛
.
Don’t worry, I also included some treat meals. 😋
.
Recipes are also conveniently portioned to 1 or 2 servings, so it’s great for college students living in a dorm, or frequent travelers/van lifers, like me! It’s perfect for parents because it’s fun for the kids, as well as busy bees because the mini waffle maker heats in just seconds & cooks most of the recipes in this book in just a few minutes! 🙌
.
Get my Waffly Fit Cookbook AND the @bydash mini waffle maker together in a perfectly packaged gift set for JUST $24.99! 😀
.
You can also buy my book by itself for $19.99 🙌
.
Watch the full video for more info & to see the book in action! And visit my website (clairepthomas.com). Click the link in my bio to purchase directly. 🙌
.
Love you all a waffle lot! Thank you so much for your support. 💛🧇 
.

.

node.text:
Choosing to live in a van means choosing a different kind of life - houseless but not homeless, tiny, resourceful, contained & always moving.
.
Choosing to live in a van means choosing freedom. It means chasing down dreams, sunsets, overnight parking & WiFi (or the absence of it).
.
Choosing to live in a van is choosing to live with less, but oh, I have acquired so much more. Tangible things matter so much less to me now. I’m collecting imaginary bookshelves full of my memories.
.
Choosing to live in a van is choosing to soak in every little moment - because before I know it, we are off again & might never be back. I know that this way of life is only temporary, it’s fleeing from me every day. I’m holding onto it as if I’ll be stationary tomorrow - as if I won’t even be here tomorrow, because right now is the only thing that’s truly guaranteed. & if I live to see another day, I know that I won’t be stationary anytime soon. After 15 months on the road, I feel like I’m just getting started on this journey. 
.
Choosing to live in a van with my man was my favorite decision I ever made.
.
.
.

My NEW CPT Fuel Good Guide is available NOW!! 🥑🍎🥦🫐🧇🌮🍕🍔🥗🍦🍪
.
I am SCREAMING with excitement you guys! I poured my heart into this nutrition E-book & I’m so happy to finally offer it to you. 🤗
.
When you fuel good, you feel good!
.
My brand new CPT Fuel Good Guide includes:
.
🍓Recipes to 80+ of my favorite delicious, healthy & easy breakfasts, entrees, desserts, side dishes, snacks, & shakes
.
🍟 Grocery list, including all the specific brands I buy
.
🥪 All of the nutrition tips, tricks & strategies that I personally live by
.
🍰 Help understanding macronutrients & the breakdown of protein, carbs & fat
.
🧀 Macro calculating/tracking advice
.
💊 Supplement recommendations
 .
🗓 Weekly meal planner
.
This is an e-book; therefore, it can be easily downloaded to your phone or any device & taken wherever you go! It will be emailed to you shortly after your purchase.
.
Our energy, our mood, our skin, our personality, & our body composition are ALL greatly impacted by what is on the end of our fork. As someone who battled & overcame an eating disorder, I understand that following a healthy & balanced diet is far from easy. I used to believe that performing & looking my best meant that I had to under-eat the same boring foods over & over again. I learned the hard way that restricting my food only restricted me further from my goals & from my happiness.
.
My life changed immensely when I began to create healthy & sustainable habits with food. I discovered how FUN cooking actually is, & that it is possible to love food AND love my body at the same time. More importantly, I discovered my passion & desire to help other people create healthier relationships with food & fitness, too.
.
I hope that this guide helps you create a healthier relationship with food & that it teaches you how to view & use food as fuel to accelerate you closer to your goals & the happiest version of yourself!
.
✨Learn more on my site, clairepthomas.com or click the link in my bio ✨
.
Tag someone who needs this guide in their life!!
.
Love you guys so much! 💛
.
#teamcpt #fuelgood #nutritioncoach #nutritiontips #healthyrecipes #healthyfood #fuelyourbody #foodisfuel #iamstphorm

node.text:
It’s time for another #clairecorechallenge! 💪 Try it for a chance to win this week’s GIVEAWAY! 👊
.
Happy Sunday guys! I’m excited to bring my weekly core challenges back after a couple weeks off due to my apparel launch. 
.
One lucky person who tries this workout will receive a free CPT Fit Guide of choice!
.
All you have to do is film yourself ATTEMPTING (it doesn’t have to look pretty 😆) this workout, tag me on your story & use the hashtag, #clairecorechallenge 💪 The more bloopers the better. 🤗
.
I do NOT choose the winner based on how well or how many reps. The weekly winner will be selected completely randomly from the pool of people who tag me throughout each week! 🙌
.
This is definitely one of my tougher challenges yet! How many reps can you get before letting go for all 3 exercises?! Rest 2-3 minutes between each, or until you feel really recovered, so that you can crush the next exercise.
.
1️⃣ FLUTTER TOES TO BAR
2️⃣ SINGLE LEG ALT. LEG RAISES + HOLD
3️⃣ SINGLE LEG ALT. CROSS BODY T2B
.
I’m really curious to see who completes this! 🤗 Even if you know you won’t be able to, TRY IT ANYWAYS. Failure only makes you tougher. It’s when we fail that we grow. 
.
Go get after this one & tag your homies who also need to try for a chance to win one of my online training programs. 💪
.
To learn more about all the programs I offer, click the link in my bio for my website!
.
I will announce the winner on my story next weekend!
.
GOOD LUCK! 😘
.
PS: please say a prayer for my snake plant 🌱😂
.
.
.
#teamcpt #corechallenge #sixpack #workoutchallenge #challengeyourself #absworkout #coreworkout #toestobar #fitnessmotivation #iamstphorm

node.text:
It might be 86 degrees in Oregon today, but that ain’t stopping me from twinning with my niece because she wanted to wear my beanie. 🥰
.
Fall is just around the corner! This waffle-knit beanie with a waffle patch will keep you waffly warm when the weather gets cold. See what I did there? 😆🧇 It’s cozy, comfortable & classic, made with a stretchy knit design. It has a fold-over cuff & is finished with a genuine leather patch. One size fits most (including 16 month olds apparently). ☺️
.
My own Mama packages & ships all of your orders & they continue to be handled with so much love & care. It’s incredibly cool that my mom is involved. She loves it as she has always been my number one fan. I am so dang grateful for her & I just had to share a bit of what goes on behind the scenes. I’m here in Oregon this week & it has been so fun getting my hands on your packages & giving each order an extra personal touch. I’m training Paislee to be Nana’s new assistant. 💛 
.
These beanies are just one piece of my limited edition apparel that I launched last week. Once they sell out, they are gone forever!
.
PS: I ship to the US, Canada, the UK, Mexico & Australia! 🙌
.
Shop all my apparel & training programs with the link in my bio. 😘
.
.
.

node.text:
From the Redwood forest to the Gulf Stream waters; This land was made for you and me. 🌲🌊
.
What a week! Here’s a little photo/video dump to sum it up!
.
We’ve been to 4 states in 8 days! After living out of our backpacks for 3 weeks, we flew 2400 miles from Oahu to San Fran. 🏝🌉 We met up with our amazing friends to tour the city & drink grapes in wine country. 🍷 We then picked up Penny (🚐) from the shipyard (we shipped her back from Maui) & drove 700+ miles up the coastline to my hometown in Oregon. 🌊 Along the way we stopped at Glass Beach in Fort Bragg, a place I have been dreaming about since I was a kid. We proceeded to Redwood National Park & were humbled & astounded as we hiked beneath such gentle giants. 🌲
.
Today, we continued on the road North, to Washington, to pick up my baby niece. 💛 I’ll be soaking in every moment with my family for the next few days until we hit the road again.
.
Life is such a beautiful ride. I’m so grateful for a roof over my head & wheels under my bed. 🚐
.
Happy Friday, friends. What are ya’ll getting yourselves into this weekend??
.
.
.

➖40 AIR SQUATS
➖50 MTN CLIMBERS

.
Comment below your score & tag your workout homies who you challenge to crush it, too! 👊

.
.

Start September off on the right foot..& on the left with my STEPtember Challenge! 👟🥾👠
.
Join me & take a minimum of 10,000 steps every day this month.🙌
.
You’ll be eligible to win some awesome giveaways coming up when you tag me in their daily steps & use the hashtag #STEPtemberchallenge 💛
.
These are just some of the amazing steps I took over the past few months that lead me to some of my favorite views. Even though I follow a workout regimen & explore outside often, I’m actually a sedentary person. I spend the majority of my days sitting on my butt doing laptop work or driving in the van. 🚐💻
.
I know I’m not the only one who could use some more movement in my life, which is why I’m excited to bring this challenge back for the second year in a row!
.
Walking/jogging is one of my favorite forms of exercise because it’s available to most people. You don't need any special equipment other than some supportive shoes & it’s a great way to spend more time outdoors. Walking alone can help reduce your risk of heart disease, obesity, diabetes, high blood pressure & depression. 😊
.
Here are ideas for fitting more walking into your routine:
.
👟Take the dog for a walk. If you don't have a dog, find a friend with a dog & steal it! Or just join them. 😉
.
👟listen to music, a book or a podcast.
.
👟Include the family. Instead of an after dinner movie, go for a sunset walk or hike together.
.
👟Walk while waiting. Take a walk instead of sitting when you're early for an appointment or waiting for a flight.
.
👟Schedule workday walks. Put reminders in your phone for short walking breaks to ramp up your energy throughout the day. Have a phone meeting? Walk & talk.
.
👟Park farther away
.
👟Take the stairs
.
See my “STEPtember” highlight for a calendar I made for you to share every day on your story if you participate in this Challenge.🤗
.
Comment below if you’re in & the friends you challenge to join you for the next 30 days!
.
Let's STEP IT UP!👊
.
#teamcpt #10ksteps #10000steps #fitchallenge #fitnesschallenge #1stphorm #walkmore #hiking #movementismedicine #vanlife

High intensity lunge circuit straight outta my Home Body Guide! 💪
.
After 3 weeks of waiting for my van to ship from Maui to Cali, we are finally on the road again! 🚐🙌
.
We are taking the next couple of days to drive the coastline up to my hometown in Oregon. We’re takin the scenic route, which means we aren’t near any gyms. That’s perfectly okay with me, though, because the outdoors is way better than a gym (in my opinion) & I’ve got my best piece of equipment with me (my body, baby!) 💁🏼‍♀️
.
High intensity bodyweight workouts have been HUGE in my routine over the past year. Not only because gyms shut down, but because traveling in a van takes me to remote places. And honestly, I just don’t enjoy spending much time in gyms anymore like I once did. My new favorite thing is discovering amazing places workout in the most beautiful gym of all, nature. 😍
.
If you travel often or if you don’t have access to a gym or if you just don’t have the time or desire to go all the time, you’ll love my 8-week Home bodyweight Guides.🤗
.
For more info, click the link in my bio, see my highlights, or go to www.clairepthomas.com 💛
.

.
Wait until the very end of the last clip if you need a giggle. 🐿
.

.
.

node.text:
I challenge you. For one minute, walk outside, stand there, breathe in silence, look up at the sky & contemplate how beautiful life is & how lucky you are to get this one chance to live.
.
Your sky might be cloudy right now, but remember, the most beautiful sunsets need those clouds to paint the sky with an array of gorgeous colors.
.
And even when the sun goes down & the sky gets dark, a new day is just around the bend & the sun will be there to rise again.
.
I’m still completely mesmerized by this sunset from one of our last nights in Maui, last week. I was so spoiled with this view & I made time to watch the sun kiss the ocean nearly every night for the last 6 months. It became my therapy. Golden hour is now my happy hour. Other than the people, this right here is what I miss the most. But, like the sun, I will back. Like the moon & the tides, I am pulled to this place & I’ll never be the same again. ☀️🌊 
.
Where’s your favorite place to watch the sunset or sunrise?
.
.
.
